                        New security challenges – new strategic concept
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Ministry of Defence, 01.10.2010]</p>
                <p>- The financial crisis [...] will affect the assumptions on which NATO’s new Strategic Concept is being based, says Minister of Defence Grete Faremo.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
