                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 23.09.2010]</p>
                <p>The entry into force of the Comprehensive Test Ban Treaty (CTBT)is within reach, Foreign Minister Støre said in his address to the CBT Ministerial Meeting in New York 23 September. </p>
                
                
