                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 23.09.2010]</p>
                <p>Norwegian design is no longer a well-kept secret. Thanks to initiatives such as the exhibition ‘100% Norway’, young designers and established design-orientated companies have both had the opportunity to show their work to an international audience, writes Foreign Minister Støre.   </p>
                
                
