                <p>This brochure will introduce you to the business opportunities in the Tromsø region, one of the fastest growing in Norway and the regional centre for the whole of North Norway. Tromsø is home to many potential partners for investigating new horizons, Foreign Minister Støre writes in his foreword to a Norway Exports' publication.</p>
                
                
